Displays an {@link https://ace.c9.io|Ace editor} in read-only mode for various source-code data types.  Utilizes the {@link https://github.com/angular-ui/ui-ace|ui-ace} angular directive wrapper.  Optionally can simply render without ace editor if "abbreviated" parameter is present.

@param {Object|string} [displayTheme] - name of theme to use for editor (if string), or an object mapping the type descriptors "applicable" value ('clientside','serverside' or 'default') to theme name.
@param {boolean} [abbreviated] - if true, simply renders as text without using Ace editor and fancy formatting.
